    <chapter id="limits-on-use">
        <title>Limits on Use of Output</title>
        <para>There are no limits on what you can do with the charts, or output you create in @PROJECT_LONGNAME@.
            However we would appreciate it if you included a credit in any patterns, or publications where you used this software.
            For example: Charts created with @PROJECT_LONGNAME@ by @PROJECT_VENDOR@.
        </para>
    </chapter>
    
